Mahogany trees are trees that may be grown with the Farming skill. Level 55 farmers may grow a mahogany tree by planting a mahogany sapling in a hardwood tree patch using a spade. The nearby squirrel will watch over a growing mahogany tree in exchange for 25 Yanillian hops, which may be noted.

A mahogany tree sapling will take 3 days, 13 hours and 20 minutes to grow to mature. Once mature, the tree grows into a mahogany tree which can be harvested for mahogany logs.

Planting a mahogany sapling in a hardwood tree patch grants 68 Farming experience. Checking the health of a mahogany tree grants 15,720 Farming experience.

'''Mahogany trees''' are trees that may be grown with the [[Farming]] [[skill]]. Level 55 farmers may grow a mahogany tree by planting a [[mahogany sapling]] in a [[hardwood tree patch]] using a [[spade]]. The nearby squirrel will watch over a growing mahogany tree in exchange for 25 [[Yanillian hops]], which may be noted.

A mahogany tree sapling will take 3 days, 13 hours and 20 minutes to grow to mature. Once mature, the tree grows into a [[mahogany]] tree which can be harvested for [[mahogany logs]].

Planting a mahogany sapling in a hardwood tree patch grants 68 Farming [[experience]]. Checking the health of a mahogany tree grants 15,720 Farming experience.
